<ab facs="#facs_254_r2l9">
<del rend="strikethrough">hat vns </del> der
                            <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vor vns cʒu den
                            <expan>heılıge<ex>n</ex></expan> behabt hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_254_r2l11">
<del rend="strikethrough">vvie </del> daʒ <add><ab facs="#facs_254_r2l10">die </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> das <expan>egeſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> veſʒlein
